<template>
  <el-steps :active="2">
    <el-step title="简历审核" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="基础信息咨询" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="面试" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="就业协议书" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="招聘完成" description=""></el-step>
  </el-steps>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  beforeCreate() {
    if(this.$route.query.rpId == undefined) {
      this.$router.push({
        path: '/GraduateEmploymentNeed',
        query: {
          notice: true
        }
      })
      // this.$notify({
      //   title: '提示',
      //   message: '请选择某一招聘过程',
      //   iconClass: 'el-icon-tickets'
      // })
    }
  },

  mounted() {

  },

  data() {
    return {
      tableData: [
        {
          enId: '1',
          graduateId: '6',
          rpPhase: '简历审核'
        }]
    }
  },

  methods: {
    goto(row) {
      this.$router.push({
        path: '/GraduateRecruitmentProcess',
        query: {
          id:1
        }
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
